{"tid":2356150,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國直播主疑迫智障女除衫開Live 涉性犯罪遭警方拘捕","createTime":"2021-01-06T15:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T01:24:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b871caecb9da4d8de6251919a684548a2425355c","tid":2356150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"BJ Ddaeng Cho疑強迫智障人士除衫開Live而引起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n近年YouTuber及直播主興起，不少人為增加人氣而各出奇謀，當中AfreecaTV的男直播主BJ Ddaeng Cho（音譯），就因於直播時，涉嫌對智障人士進行性犯罪而引起爭議，更遭警方拘捕調查。<br />\n<br />\n有暴露鏡頭<br />\nBJ Ddaeng Cho早前進行「脫衣直播」，而且用了「汽車旅館」、「火熱的晚上」等關鍵詞為直播的標題。片中BJ Ddaeng Cho帶一名女性A某到汽車旅館一起開直播，當中有A某部份身體被暴露的鏡頭，二人聊天過程中亦不斷出現有關性方面的發言。據知A某有表達拒絕開「脫衣直播」的意思，但BJ Ddaeng Cho以強硬的態度進行直播節目。<br />\n<br />\n疑獨佔直播收益<br />\n事後有網民踢爆A某是智力障礙達到三級的人士，而且BJ Ddaeng Cho涉嫌獨佔直播中的收益，因此網民紛紛批評BJ Ddaeng Cho利用智障人士賺錢，質疑他強迫認知水平只有6歲左右的女生「賣淫」，留言指BJ Ddaeng Cho「是性罪犯」、「應該受到處罰」等。<br />\n<br />\n自稱是戀人關係<br />\nBJ Ddaeng Cho今早回應：「我是在得到這位朋友（A某）同意的情況下才進行節目，因為觀眾喜歡刺激的東西，所以選擇了『火熱的晚上』這個充滿刺激性的詞語，沒想到事情會鬧大、會變成這樣。」BJ Ddaeng Cho又表示是真心喜歡A某，二人是拍拖的關係，又指以為觀眾會喜歡這類節目，解釋：「剛開始不知道是錯的，但好像是我越線了。以後絕對不會做那種事了，以後會和女朋友愉快地繼續做節目。」對於「性犯罪」的指控，BJ Ddaeng Cho表示：「她肯定會在那種情況下說不願意做，她在開播前就表達了想要做直播的意思，絕對沒有做出A某討厭的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n而京畿南部警察廳的網絡調查隊，今日就緊急拘捕了BJ Ddaeng Cho，並正進行調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/439zk53A3fmIVuOaHsqhPgKHabo=/802x482/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DQ2EJE44FFGVFO2YGC7V5SM6KU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F439zk53A3fmIVuOaHsqhPgKHabo%3D%2F802x482%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDQ2EJE44FFGVFO2YGC7V5SM6KU.jpg&h=ab66bb20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UCDPCAVXV1pe8LEMMwb-iy6epB8=/802x532/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GSBJMAAVKFEJ3PALUBEGW72ENU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUCDPCAVXV1pe8LEMMwb-iy6epB8%3D%2F802x532%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGSBJMAAVKFEJ3PALUBEGW72ENU.JPG&h=3a1edfbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J_X6BUfJOG4Pit96SHacpcKCxCk=/802x531/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4ZIY4673ZZAIVAOFON54PJXL3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ_X6BUfJOG4Pit96SHacpcKCxCk%3D%2F802x531%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4ZIY4673ZZAIVAOFON54PJXL3U.jpg&h=7baee526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210106/TDRFZQ3NK5BHXJGZ7R7EUHGY3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210106%2FTDRFZQ3NK5BHXJGZ7R7EUHGY3I%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5oVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d64ea064\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210106%2FTDRFZQ3NK5BHXJGZ7R7EUHGY3I%2F&h=e6c0bf89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210106/TDRFZQ3NK5BHXJGZ7R7EUHGY3I/</a>"},{"pid":"5f676c8614824e8a85f4007201e4d7433f39d50d","tid":2356150,"uid":93096,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"痴撚線..."},{"pid":"c43c90c06f92912431330a8295291bdbb38a839e","tid":2356150,"uid":40272,"like":7,"dislike":33,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"片呢"},{"pid":"a81d02ee2cf911388c3f3b5bdede6dc8dd5cead0","tid":2356150,"uid":16659,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"quote":{"pid":"5f676c8614824e8a85f4007201e4d7433f39d50d","tid":2356150,"uid":93096,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"痴撚線..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:1